title: FOG Featuring Jeff Chimenti 05/15/14 San Rafael California
description:
FOG - CD Release Party.

Featuring Brian Melvin, Jeff Chimenti, Brad Buethe and Peter Barshay
Thursday May 15th 2014, Live @ The Fenix in San Rafael California.


Fog is an eclectic jazz quartet made up of Jeff Chimenti (keys), Brad
Buethe (guitar), Peter Barshay (stand up bass), and Brian Melvin (drums).  
Using jazz as a skeletal format, they blend songs from many genres and
composers, as well as original compositions.
